text: The men's 50 metres breaststroke at the 2018 World Para Swimming European Championships was held at the National Aquatic Centre in Dublin from 13 - 19 August. A single classification final was held in all over this event. ==Medalists== {| |- |SB3 2018 World Para Swimming European Championships SB3 Dublin 2018 Results book | || 49.03 | || 55.06 | || 59.44 |- |colspan=7| |- |- bgcolor= e8e8e8 |colspan=7| |} ==See also== *List of IPC world records in swimming ==References== 50 metres breaststroke
